headline: Why Cloudflare (NET) Stock Is Jumping Today
summary: Cloud services provider Cloudflare (NET) is rallying 8% today after Truist, a bank, raised its price target on NET stock. Why Truist Is Bullish on NET The bank increased its price target on NET to $140 from $120, with the shares currently trading around $137.
